"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1931704-Olympics-2024-Novak-Djokovic-Matthew-Ebden-John-Peers\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  A lot can happen in one week, as Australia's Matthew Ebden learned at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 85, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 35, \"end\": 44, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.46469075292670087, \"rank\": 0.8023832605841773, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 47, \"end\": 60, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Ebden\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matthew Ebden\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Ebden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Ebden\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The doubles world No.\", \"from\": 86, \"to\": 107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"3 got into the singles draw as an alternate following withdrawals and was thrashed by Novak Djokovic 6-0 6-1.\", \"from\": 108, \"to\": 217, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 194, \"end\": 208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Immediately after the match, Ebdenannounced that he had officially retired from singles tennisand turned his attention to the men's doubles draw with John Peers.\", \"from\": 219, \"to\": 380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 369, \"end\": 379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Peers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"John Peers\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Peers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Peers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Seven days later, the Aussies won an Olympic gold medal, coming from a set and break down to beat Austin Krajicek and Rajeev Ram of the USA in a match tiebreak 6-7(6) 7-6(1) [10-8].\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 480, \"end\": 495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austin_Krajicek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Austin Krajicek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austin_Krajicek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austin_Krajicek\"}, {\"begin\": 500, \"end\": 510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajeev_Ram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rajeev Ram\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajeev_Ram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajeev_Ram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ebden looked lost on the court when he came out to face top seed Djokovic in singles last Saturday.\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It took 46 minutes for him to win his first and only game of the match after training 0-6 0-4.\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 759, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Early in the second set,he even resorted to trying to quit the match, jokingly handing his racket to a spectator so he could sub out.\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 893, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 36-year-old had not played a singles match in almost two years, since an outing in the qualifying rounds of the ATP 250 event in Winston-Salem.\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 1042, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1028, \"end\": 1041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winston-Salem_Open\", \"score\": 0.9999980145545734, \"rank\": 1.985427683386114e-06, \"text\": \"Winston-Salem\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winston-Salem_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winston-Salem_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And he officially quit the game afterwards.\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1086, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Safe to say I am officially retired from singles after that,\\\" he wrote onInstagram.\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1171, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After turning his attention back to his real specialism, doubles, he managed to win his first gold medal alongside compatriot and neighbour Peers.\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1319, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After securing the win, Ebden confessed that his loss to Djokovic was on his mind. \\\"\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1377, \"end\": 1385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.907967326476901e-26, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Honestly, yes.\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1419, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think last night, I did think of it a bit,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just in:Olympic gold medallist 'really sad' after 'destroying friendship' with victory    Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1668, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1699, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  The doubles star was even pre-planning a celebratory social media post.\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1795, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was actually dreaming of an Instagram post like how it started, how it's going.\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1878, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1827, \"end\": 1836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.646854929536401e-27, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was thinking of my score [seven] days ago, winning one game, and then I was thinking swipe right and there is a gold medal photo.\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 2010, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe I will have to make that post at some point,\\\" he laughed.\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2074, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ebden also revealed that he defied orders from Australia's tennis captain for the Olympics, Lleyton Hewitt, to get the chance to officially see off his singles career.\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2123, \"end\": 2132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.46469075292670087, \"rank\": 0.8023832605841773, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2168, \"end\": 2182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lleyton_Hewitt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lleyton Hewitt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lleyton_Hewitt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lleyton_Hewitt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He continued: \\\"I did come off that singles match fully focused on the doubles.\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2322, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Literally when I got the call up to play [singles], Lleyton was like, 'No do not play, you save your body, make sure do not get injured.\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2459, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are not here for that, I want a medal in the doubles or the mixed, whatever.'\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I said, 'Okay, I will play but I promise I will not get injured.'\", \"from\": 2543, \"to\": 2613, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So my main goal that match was just not to get injured and I did that, had a hit, had some fun.\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Got to officially retire from singles which was nice.\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2763, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My wife was liking that, I never officially played my last official retirement singles match and she thought I deserved a nice little match like that.\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2914, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So that was a nice little miracle that happened to say goodbye to my singles career.\\\"\", \"from\": 2915, \"to\": 3000, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Djokovic sends threat to Alcaraz as Serb seeks revenge for Wimbledon  Do not miss:Tennis star defaulted and booed after throwing racket and swearing at fan  Do not miss:Djokovic defies injury to reach first Olympics final and set Alcaraz rematch  We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 3002, \"to\": 3370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3039, \"end\": 3046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.732834497928757e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 3050, \"end\": 3054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.934618666305423, \"rank\": 0.0697030808465419, \"text\": \"Serb\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}, {\"begin\": 3244, \"end\": 3251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.732834497928757e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3447, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 3448, \"to\": 3480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy    His focus on the doubles paid off, and Ebden and Peers walked away with their first gold medal.\", \"from\": 3481, \"to\": 3602, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peers had previously won bronze in the mixed doubles with Ash Barty in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 3603, \"to\": 3680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3661, \"end\": 3670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashleigh_Barty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ash Barty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashleigh_Barty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashleigh_Barty\"}, {\"begin\": 3674, \"end\": 3679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9888034944507593, \"rank\": 0.011295339895001219, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ebden added: \\\"It's more than a dream, I did not even dream of winning a gold medal growing up or whatever.\", \"from\": 3681, \"to\": 3787, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The last few years, had great success on the doubles court and it gave me a lot of belief and confidence coming in here.\", \"from\": 3788, \"to\": 3908, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We spoke a few months ago about our partnership, our best chance to win and he said, what are you looking for?\", \"from\": 3910, \"to\": 4021, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I said looking for our best chance to win.\", \"from\": 4022, \"to\": 4064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We believed in ourselves, we started a few months ago already thinking and preparing about this.\", \"from\": 4065, \"to\": 4161, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even all week here, all the tough matches so I am super happy to get the reward because you do not always get the reward for all of your hard work, but when you do it's pretty sweet.\\\"\", \"from\": 4162, \"to\": 4345, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 4347, \"to\": 4516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4484, \"end\": 4497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.707262443564938e-25, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 4518, \"to\": 4585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4533, \"end\": 4546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.707262443564938e-25, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"